{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "d730fd51-c02f-4af5-a05d-47f3e1f26ccb",
    "name": "Healthcare Platform - Real-Time Booking API",
    "description": "Complete Postman collection for Real-Time Booking System. Patients can create instant booking requests that are sent to nearby providers. Providers receive notifications and can accept bookings in real-time. Includes emergency booking support, location-based matching, and auto-expiration after 15 minutes.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "37469907"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Patient - Create Booking Requests",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create Emergency Doctor Request",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    const response = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (response.data && response.data._id) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('BOOKING_ID', response.data._id);",
                  "        console.log('Booking ID:', response.data._id);",
                  "        console.log('Status:', response.data.status);",
                  "        console.log('Notified Providers:', response.data.notifiedProviders.length);",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{PATIENT_TOKEN}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"serviceType\": \"doctor\",\n  \"description\": \"Severe chest pain and difficulty breathing. Need immediate medical attention.\",\n  \"urgency\": \"emergency\",\n  \"preferredTime\": \"2026-04-11T12:00:00.000Z\",\n  \"specialRequirements\": \"Cardiologist preferred. Patient has history of heart disease.\",\n  \"address\": \"123 Main Street, Apartment 5B, New York, NY 10001\",\n  \"coordinates\": [-73.9352, 40.7306],\n  \"isEmergency\": true,\n  \"notes\": \"Patient is 65 years old, diabetic, on blood pressure medication.\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{BASE_URL}}/realtime-bookings/create",
              "host": [
                "{{BASE_URL}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "realtime-bookings",
                "create"
              ]
            },
            "description": "**Create Emergency Doctor Request**\n\nPatient creates an urgent booking request for immediate medical attention. This endpoint:\n- Creates real-time booking with 15-minute auto-expiration\n- Finds nearby doctors within 10km radius\n- Sends push notifications to all nearby providers\n- Marks as emergency for priority handling\n- Returns list of notified providers\n\n**Service Types:**\n- doctor\n- nurse\n- ambulance\n- pharmacist\n- bloodbank\n- pathology\n\n**Urgency Levels:**\n- low: Non-urgent, flexible timing\n- medium: Standard priority (default)\n- high: Urgent, need soon\n- emergency: Critical, immediate attention\n\n**Location:**\n- address: Full address string\n- coordinates: [longitude, latitude] for geo-matching\n\n**Auto-Expiration:**\n- Booking expires after 15 minutes if no provider accepts\n- Status changes to 'expired' automatically\n- Patient receives notification to create new request"
          },
          "response": []
        },
