              "host": [
                "{{BASE_URL}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "realtime-bookings",
                "{{BOOKING_ID}}",
                "accept"
              ]
            },
            "description": "**Accept Booking Request**\n\nProvider accepts a pending booking request. This endpoint:\n- Changes booking status to 'accepted'\n- Sets acceptedProvider to current provider\n- Records acceptance timestamp\n- Sends notification to patient\n- Prevents other providers from accepting (first-come-first-served)\n- Returns 409 error if already accepted by another provider\n\n**After Acceptance:**\n- Provider should update status to 'on_the_way' when traveling\n- Then 'in_progress' when service starts\n- Finally 'completed' when service ends"
          },
          "response": []
        },
